Dialogue: 0,0:43:09.01,0:43:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. It's okay to just be rather than to do or have.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:13.38,0:43:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,The other levels of consciousness
