Dialogue: 0,0:43:36.34,0:43:39.65,Default,,0,0,0,,end it's what you have become. It's what you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.26,0:43:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Surrender your will to God and therefore you can let
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.86,0:43:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,bygones be bygones.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.92,0:43:53.01,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandmother used to say on the maternal side,
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.01,0:43:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,she'd say she was saintly. In fact, she was considered for sainthood.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.51,0:44:02.38,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have anything good to say about a person,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.73,0:44:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,then don't say anything at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.25,0:44:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you'll see the mind really likes to
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.13,0:44:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,say things that are not too complimentary about people.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:15.86,0:44:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what gossip is all about. And when I was
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.21,0:44:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,young in the church,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.17,0:44:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the women's organizations in the church,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.30,0:44:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,their main problem, their main character defect that they all worked on
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.07,0:44:32.59,Default,,0,0,0,,was the attractiveness of gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.09,0:44:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,And I worked in a, I worked in a,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:38.07,0:44:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,something about gardening, I forget the name of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:44:40.09,0:44:44.13,Default,,0,0,0,,greenhouse one time. And there was five or six women and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:44.80,0:44:47.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. And all they did all day was gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.40,0:44:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all they did. They didn't have TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.44,0:44:54.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.11,0:44:54.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.42,0:44:57.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So look at gossip, obviously, as a source of amusement.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:57.48,0:44:59.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure if they had television, they would have turned it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.32,0:45:03.11,Default,,0,0,0,,But the conversation went, did you see the way Gertrude looked at him?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:04.38,0:45:05.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And did you see what she was wearing?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.92,0:45:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,She wore the same thing last time, you know,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.69,0:45:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the way the whole thing went.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.50,0:45:13.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And I listened to that for eight hours as I stuck these seedlings in.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.69,0:45:17.51,Default,,0,0,0,,So I got an enormous education in gossip.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:22.46,0:45:26.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have anything good to say about a person, then say nothing at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.98,0:45:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, otherwise, the first negative thing you can see people run,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.03,0:45:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,did you hear that so-and-so got a ticket for so-and-so?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.11,0:45:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-huh. He got a ticket for driving drunk, I hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.09,0:45:41.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. No wonder his wife is saying, you know, I didn't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.09,0:45:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:47.86,0:45:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,It's important to realize that mankind has been at war
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.44,0:45:54.01,Default,,0,0,0,,93% of recorded history.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.53,0:45:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,93% of time, man has been at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.63,0:46:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, I don't remember how many wars we got going on in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:05.71,0:46:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The United States has two of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.36,0:46:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,But since I've been in the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:10.53,0:46:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,when I first was born, World War I wasn't quite, it was just over.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.71,0:46:21.15,Default,,0,0,0,,And the shell-shocked war veterans were wandering around looking for jobs, etc.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.03,0:46:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,And then since I've been around, I've lived through, I don't know, six or seven wars.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.11,0:46:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been one war after another.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.57,0:46:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,If you count little wars,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:31.40,0:46:33.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Africa and various places,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:33.88,0:46:38.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I guess it's been, there's been a war all the time I've been alive this lifetime.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.21,0:46:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So for 82 years, at least I know,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.09,0:46:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,man has been at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:45.90,0:46:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually several wars at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:51.98,0:46:53.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So what do you think of that?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:55.48,0:46:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,So there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:56.36,0:46:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:00.76,0:47:01.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.48,0:47:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:05.17,0:47:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Mankind has been at war almost all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.15,0:47:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The only time...
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.78,0:47:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,The only time he wasn't at war, he was probably sick with the plague
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.53,0:47:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,and too sick to be at war.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:14.55,0:47:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Or too impoverished, he couldn't even afford to buy a Tommy Hawk.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:23.34,0:47:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,I share this with Brock once in a while.
