Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.67,0:47:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.46,0:47:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The news in the morning is that something other happened, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:33.05,0:47:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And I'd say, well, so there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.80,0:47:37.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:38.17,0:47:40.63,Default,,0,0,0,,In a way, that's being fatalistic.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:41.51,0:47:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,So there you are means that's the way the world runs.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.80,0:47:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the way things are in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:50.38,0:47:54.53,Default,,0,0,0,,That infuriates the gooders who feel that they shouldn't be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.40,0:47:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It shouldn't be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.40,0:48:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,I accept the fact that there will be lots of people in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.34,0:48:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,who say it shouldn't be that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.36,0:48:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,But it is that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.42,0:48:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.86,0:48:12.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.78,0:48:17.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Another way to explain it is what will be will be.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.38,0:48:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,And what will be will be is not just chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.11,0:48:22.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Ha, ha, ha, ha.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:22.59,0:48:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What will be will be is very hard to describe verbally.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.01,0:48:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,It has to do with the influence of karmic influences.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:31.44,0:48:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, karmic influence, it's like we're all little magnetic,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.94,0:48:40.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we're all little like pieces of iron filings
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.32,0:48:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,with a magnetic north pole and south pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:44.26,0:48:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,And the infinite field of consciousness, which is the mind of God,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.00,0:48:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,is an infinite magnetic field.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.55,0:48:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Now,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.78,0:48:55.19,Default,,0,0,0,,what you have become
Dialogue: 0,0:48:55.19,0:48:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,determines where you are within that field.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.63,0:49:03.75,Default,,0,0,0,,So you've got to picture yourself as an iron filing.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.98,0:49:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You've got a north pole and a south pole.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:08.19,0:49:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Here's this big, powerful electromagnetic field,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:11.40,0:49:13.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the mind of God, called consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:14.82,0:49:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, where you are within the field
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.67,0:49:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,depends on the decisions that you make.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:19.55,0:49:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,So as you say, well, I'll forgive that person,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.90,0:49:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you move up here higher in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.80,0:49:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And if you say, I'm going to get even with that son of a bitch,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.51,0:49:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you move down in the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.46,0:49:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,See, you can't blame it on God.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.40,0:49:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,See, what historical religions do is blame it on God.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.40,0:49:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,This creates a lot of atheists in the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.90,0:49:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, what happens to you is solely up to you alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:47.51,0:49:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I forgive him, I hate him.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:52.42,0:49:53.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, overlook it.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.48,0:49:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,No, get even.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:55.71,0:49:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You can see how a little electromagnetic iron filing,
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.71,0:50:01.09,Default,,0,0,0,,how you move,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.09,0:50:02.82,Default,,0,0,0,,and the infinite magnetic field,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.34,0:50:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the infinite power of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.21,0:50:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of consciousness is beyond man's imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.30,0:50:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We've quoted a scientific explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.01,0:50:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The energy, the power,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.01,0:50:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,one cubic centimeter of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.50,0:50:26.78,Default,,0,0,0,,is greater than its equivalent as weight of the entire universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:27.82,0:50:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,One cubic inch of the infinite field of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.73,0:50:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,is equivalent to the power of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.69,0:50:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,One is greater than the total mass of the entire universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.55,0:50:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The entire mass of the universe is less than the power
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.42,0:50:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of a tiny bit of consciousness.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.50,0:50:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:49.92,0:50:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Because consciousness is the field of God's will.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:55.11,0:50:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And the power of God's will is infinite,
Dialogue: 0,0:50:58.63,0:51:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,has no beginning, has no end, and is infinite.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:02.48,0:51:03.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Acceptance.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.13,0:51:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So there you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.07,0:51:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:06.53,0:51:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.38,0:51:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Develop a peaceful nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:11.94,0:51:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Be aware of the power of nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.65,0:51:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Love nature and develop yourself a peaceful nature.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:20.63,0:51:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,See the beauty of all that exists.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.42,0:51:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:24.98,0:51:26.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Value quietude.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:26.63,0:51:27.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Value quietude.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:27.80,0:51:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to turn the radio on
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.25,0:51:30.71,Default,,0,0,0,,the instant you walk into the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:34.11,0:51:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The enemy is really the inner child,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:36.84,0:51:38.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the innocence of the inner child,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:38.94,0:51:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and the inner child's willfulness,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.65,0:51:45.17,Default,,0,0,0,,as spiritual beings, we practice the virtues.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.17,0:51:47.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We don't claim perfection.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:47.17,0:51:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We claim progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.17,0:51:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We try our best to forgive people,
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.17,0:51:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,even though they seem to be evil or wrong or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.17,0:51:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We practice the virtues.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:55.17,0:51:57.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It doesn't say we master the virtues.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.17,0:51:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It says we practice them.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.17,0:52:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're admitting that we are evolutionary,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.17,0:52:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that the degree of our fulfillment,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.17,0:52:05.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of our human potential,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:05.17,0:52:07.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is not the same as the degree
Dialogue: 0,0:52:07.17,0:52:09.17,Default,,0,0,0,,of our spiritual fulfillment.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.17,0:52:11.17,Default,,0,0,0,,So we're admitting that we are evolutionary,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.17,0:52:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,that the degree of our fulfillment, of our human potential,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.51,0:52:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,is constantly growing.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.51,0:52:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Recall when you,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.80,0:52:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,this is a very good one,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:20.80,0:52:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because very often,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:22.80,0:52:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the power of this arises in childhood.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.82,0:52:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Recall peace on earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.82,0:52:28.82,Default,,0,0,0,,goodwill towards men,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.82,0:52:30.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the angels who announce
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.82,0:52:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,the coming of Christ
Dialogue: 0,0:52:32.82,0:52:34.98,Default,,0,0,0,,on Christmas Eve.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.98,0:52:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Strive to be angelic
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.98,0:52:38.98,Default,,0,0,0,,rather than Luciferic.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.98,0:52:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Practice no attractions and no aversions.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:41.21,0:52:43.21,Default,,0,0,0,,The Buddha said,
Dialogue: 0,0:52:43.21,0:52:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,neither attractions nor aversions.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.21,0:52:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:52:48.26,0:52:58.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going to quit.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:58.23,0:53:00.55,Default,,0,0,0,,People are afraid of death.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:00.55,0:53:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, the near-death experience
Dialogue: 0,0:53:02.55,0:53:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of absolute and total peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.55,0:53:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So the goal,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.59,0:53:08.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the lecture for today
Dialogue: 0,0:53:08.59,0:53:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,has to do with peace
Dialogue: 0,0:53:10.59,0:53:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and peacefulness.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:12.59,0:53:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,And although people fear death,
Dialogue: 0,0:53:14.59,0:53:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the actual experience
Dialogue: 0,0:53:16.59,0:53:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of infinite peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:19.03,0:53:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll stop there for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.59,0:53:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,God bless you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.03,0:53:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,We purposely came back a little late
Dialogue: 0,0:53:58.03,0:54:00.03,Default,,0,0,0,,so you wouldn't feel guilty
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.03,0:54:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,about getting back late.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.80,0:54:08.15,Default,,0,0,0,,We want everybody to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:08.15,0:54:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,102 ways to happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:12.15,0:54:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:15.50,0:54:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No attractions and no aversions.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.65,0:54:20.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That requires some discipline.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:20.65,0:54:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it by asking yourself,
Dialogue: 0,0:54:23.57,0:54:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,could I let go
Dialogue: 0,0:54:25.57,0:54:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,wanting to be attracted by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:27.57,0:54:30.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And you begin to see
Dialogue: 0,0:54:30.11,0:54:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that the attraction
Dialogue: 0,0:54:32.11,0:54:34.11,Default,,0,0,0,,is something you project
Dialogue: 0,0:54:34.11,0:54:36.11,Default,,0,0,0,,onto things.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:36.11,0:54:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,That famous book that I've mentioned
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.11,0:54:41.84,Default,,0,0,0,,a number of times
Dialogue: 0,0:54:41.84,0:54:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,called Glamour says
Dialogue: 0,0:54:43.84,0:54:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the thing is not attractive at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.96,0:54:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Its attraction is due to an energy
Dialogue: 0,0:54:48.96,0:54:53.05,Default,,0,0,0,,that you project onto it.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:53.05,0:54:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that's quite a surprise, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:55.05,0:54:57.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You think the attraction
Dialogue: 0,0:54:57.53,0:54:59.53,Default,,0,0,0,,is in the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:59.53,0:55:02.03,Default,,0,0,0,,The attraction is in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:02.03,0:55:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you're very attracted
Dialogue: 0,0:55:04.03,0:55:06.55,Default,,0,0,0,,to a doughnut
Dialogue: 0,0:55:06.55,0:55:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're hungry
Dialogue: 0,0:55:09.73,0:55:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and you like doughnuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:11.73,0:55:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't think doughnuts
Dialogue: 0,0:55:13.73,0:55:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,are attractive.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:16.32,0:55:20.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You think they're ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:20.90,0:55:24.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugly doughnuts.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:24.19,0:55:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How to be one up
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.19,0:55:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,in a conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:28.19,0:55:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to have an argument.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:30.19,0:55:32.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you an inner secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:32.19,0:55:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to have an argument
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.19,0:55:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,with somebody, see?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.19,0:55:38.19,Default,,0,0,0,,They're a debater.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.19,0:55:40.19,Default,,0,0,0,,So the debater gets up with you
Dialogue: 0,0:55:40.19,0:55:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:55:57.51,0:56:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you got something on your chin.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:02.48,0:56:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that mayonnaise?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:06.38,0:56:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to get some time.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:10.42,0:56:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,In an innocuous,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.42,0:56:14.42,Default,,0,0,0,,in a harmless situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:14.42,0:56:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Just say,
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.42,0:56:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is that something on your chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:23.03,0:56:25.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that ketchup?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.03,0:56:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:27.13,0:56:34.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that lettuce?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:34.86,0:56:36.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that mayonnaise on your chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.07,0:56:44.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So that completely throws
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.07,0:56:46.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the other person off their mindset.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:46.51,0:56:48.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Throws them off their mindset.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:48.55,0:56:50.55,Default,,0,0,0,,And then you swoop in.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:50.55,0:56:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Waiting for them
Dialogue: 0,0:56:52.94,0:56:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,like a hawk on the edge of the field.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.94,0:56:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that mayonnaise
Dialogue: 0,0:56:56.94,0:56:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,on your chin?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:01.71,0:57:04.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They've lost
Dialogue: 0,0:57:04.11,0:57:06.28,Default,,0,0,0,,the game.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:06.28,0:57:08.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You throw them off
Dialogue: 0,0:57:08.28,0:57:10.82,Default,,0,0,0,,their cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:10.82,0:57:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I learned that in boxing.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.82,0:57:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,How to pretend.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:14.82,0:57:16.82,Default,,0,0,0,,It's called the feint.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:16.82,0:57:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,And of course
Dialogue: 0,0:57:18.92,0:57:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,that was a formidable mosquito weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:20.92,0:57:24.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They didn't have mosquito weight.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.88,0:57:28.76,Default,,0,0,0,,They invented mosquito weight for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:28.76,0:57:32.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Except the social roles of others.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:32.71,0:57:34.71,Default,,0,0,0,,In other words,
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.71,0:57:36.71,Default,,0,0,0,,people are fulfilling
Dialogue: 0,0:57:36.71,0:57:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,what they see as their social role.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.71,0:57:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really actually
Dialogue: 0,0:57:40.71,0:57:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,who they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:42.75,0:57:44.75,Default,,0,0,0,,They're acting out a social role
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.75,0:57:46.75,Default,,0,0,0,,in their definition
Dialogue: 0,0:57:46.75,0:57:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,of the understanding of
Dialogue: 0,0:57:48.75,0:57:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,how they're supposed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:57:50.75,0:57:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and what they're supposed to be
Dialogue: 0,0:57:52.75,0:57:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and how they're supposed to look
Dialogue: 0,0:57:54.88,0:57:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and how they're supposed to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:56.88,0:57:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Their behavior
Dialogue: 0,0:57:58.88,0:58:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and appearance
Dialogue: 0,0:58:00.88,0:58:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and everything should be like.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:03.07,0:58:05.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So that's the value
Dialogue: 0,0:58:05.07,0:58:07.07,Default,,0,0,0,,of trying to understand others.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:07.07,0:58:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,To understand what runs them
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.07,0:58:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and out of that
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.07,0:58:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,comes compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.07,0:58:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Out of that arises compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:15.07,0:58:17.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Understanding others
Dialogue: 0,0:58:17.07,0:58:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,brings compassion.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:21.05,0:58:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,The near-death experience
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.05,0:58:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is one of total peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.17,0:58:27.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Which is hard to explain.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:27.17,0:58:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,But the peace of God
Dialogue: 0,0:58:29.17,0:58:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,that goes beyond understanding
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.17,0:58:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is a peace of
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.17,0:58:35.17,Default,,0,0,0,,great profundity.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:35.17,0:58:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Transforms
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.17,0:58:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the appearance of the world
Dialogue: 0,0:58:39.17,0:58:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,and takes you out of all
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.34,0:58:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,possible suffering.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:43.63,0:58:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, next.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:45.63,0:58:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got 101 of these.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:47.63,0:58:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We better move along.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:50.07,0:58:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Only the ego is vulnerable.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:52.07,0:58:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The real self is eternal.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:54.07,0:58:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,The real self is invisible
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.07,0:58:58.26,Default,,0,0,0,,to other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:58.26,0:59:00.26,Default,,0,0,0,,And therefore, if your feelings are hurt
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.26,0:59:02.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or you've got to have something
Dialogue: 0,0:59:02.26,0:59:04.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or win something
Dialogue: 0,0:59:04.26,0:59:06.26,Default,,0,0,0,,or you're lamenting losing something
Dialogue: 0,0:59:06.26,0:59:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,remind yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.26,0:59:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,it's only the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.26,0:59:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,creating this experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.67,0:59:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's only the ego creating this experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:14.67,0:59:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because of your relationship
Dialogue: 0,0:59:16.67,0:59:18.67,Default,,0,0,0,,to the object
Dialogue: 0,0:59:18.67,0:59:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that you mourn it when it's lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:20.84,0:59:22.96,Default,,0,0,0,,So, again
Dialogue: 0,0:59:22.96,0:59:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it's always going back to the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:59:24.96,0:59:27.07,Default,,0,0,0,,to understand the ego
Dialogue: 0,0:59:27.07,0:59:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore
Dialogue: 0,0:59:29.07,0:59:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,not be its victim.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:31.07,0:59:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Live in each instant
Dialogue: 0,0:59:33.07,0:59:35.07,Default,,0,0,0,,which is innately peaceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:35.07,0:59:37.36,Default,,0,0,0,,This comes about
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.36,0:59:39.36,Default,,0,0,0,,through spiritual work also.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:39.36,0:59:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,To live not one day at a time
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.00,0:59:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,not one hour at a time
Dialogue: 0,0:59:44.00,0:59:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,not one hour at a time
Dialogue: 0,0:59:46.00,0:59:48.00,Default,,0,0,0,,one instant at a time.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:48.00,0:59:50.57,Default,,0,0,0,,We were either going to make it
Dialogue: 0,0:59:50.57,0:59:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,back here in time
Dialogue: 0,0:59:52.57,0:59:55.30,Default,,0,0,0,,or we weren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.30,0:59:57.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:59:57.30,0:59:59.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:59.40,1:00:01.40,Default,,0,0,0,,The traffic is there
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.40,1:00:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,and helping or not helping.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.63,1:00:09.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Live in each instant.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:09.01,1:00:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,If you live in each instant
Dialogue: 0,1:00:11.01,1:00:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,you are always in peace
Dialogue: 0,1:00:13.01,1:00:15.01,Default,,0,0,0,,because suffering is created
Dialogue: 0,1:00:15.01,1:00:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,by writing a scenario
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.01,1:00:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,writing a story.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:19.01,1:00:21.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I lost
Dialogue: 0,1:00:21.59,1:00:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,poor so-and-so
Dialogue: 0,1:00:23.59,1:00:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and he got run over by a so-and-so
Dialogue: 0,1:00:25.59,1:00:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and then my cat drowned
Dialogue: 0,1:00:27.59,1:00:29.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and then the next thing you know
Dialogue: 0,1:00:29.59,1:00:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I had a flat tire
Dialogue: 0,1:00:31.59,1:00:33.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I got a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:33.59,1:00:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean you got a whole long story.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:36.03,1:00:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Now actually
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.75,1:00:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,the cop giving you a ticket
Dialogue: 0,1:00:40.75,1:00:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,you could say
Dialogue: 0,1:00:42.90,1:00:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,anytime I got a ticket
Dialogue: 0,1:00:44.90,1:00:46.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I always thanked him
Dialogue: 0,1:00:46.90,1:00:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said thank you for
Dialogue: 0,1:00:48.94,1:00:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,helping to save my life.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:50.94,1:00:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Then he'd say
Dialogue: 0,1:00:55.01,1:00:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,well I was going to write you a ticket.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:57.01,1:00:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I said I realize you're actually
Dialogue: 0,1:00:59.01,1:01:01.01,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to save my life
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.01,1:01:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'm so stupid I don't realize it.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.01,1:01:05.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The cop would say
Dialogue: 0,1:01:05.01,1:01:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,well thank you
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.01,1:01:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,watch it from now on.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:10.19,1:01:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Detach from control.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.19,1:01:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This observer.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:14.23,1:01:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a little more sophisticated.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.23,1:01:18.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It means that if you constantly
Dialogue: 0,1:01:18.23,1:01:20.23,Default,,0,0,0,,let go wanting to control things
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.23,1:01:22.23,Default,,0,0,0,,change them being on top of them
Dialogue: 0,1:01:22.23,1:01:24.26,Default,,0,0,0,,what happens is the
Dialogue: 0,1:01:24.26,1:01:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,chatter of the ego stops
Dialogue: 0,1:01:26.26,1:01:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and you then become
Dialogue: 0,1:01:28.32,1:01:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,merely the observer
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.32,1:01:32.36,Default,,0,0,0,,the witness.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:32.36,1:01:34.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Now this is a high spiritual state
Dialogue: 0,1:01:34.36,1:01:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,in which you relinquish the personal self
Dialogue: 0,1:01:36.36,1:01:38.36,Default,,0,0,0,,to the field of consciousness itself.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:38.36,1:01:40.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Witnessing and observing
Dialogue: 0,1:01:40.75,1:01:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,you think there's a you doing that
Dialogue: 0,1:01:42.75,1:01:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,there is no you
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.96,1:01:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,witnessing or observing
Dialogue: 0,1:01:46.96,1:01:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,there isn't any person there at all
Dialogue: 0,1:01:49.15,1:01:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,the idea that there's a person
Dialogue: 0,1:01:51.63,1:01:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,there comes in after you've
Dialogue: 0,1:01:53.63,1:01:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,observed and witnessed.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:55.71,1:01:57.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Observing and witnessing goes on
Dialogue: 0,1:01:57.71,1:01:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,autonomously of its own
Dialogue: 0,1:01:59.71,1:02:01.71,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't need a personal self
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.71,1:02:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't need a personal self
Dialogue: 0,1:02:03.71,1:02:05.76,Default,,0,0,0,,consciousness is
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.76,1:02:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,aware and you don't have
Dialogue: 0,1:02:08.96,1:02:10.96,Default,,0,0,0,,to interject yourself and say
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.96,1:02:12.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware. You say the edge of the
Dialogue: 0,1:02:12.96,1:02:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,stage is there
Dialogue: 0,1:02:14.96,1:02:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,the edge of the stage is there
Dialogue: 0,1:02:17.01,1:02:19.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know where the hell is the edge of the stage
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.21,1:02:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,come
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.53,1:02:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,it's there someplace
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.55,1:02:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,the edge of the stair is there
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.55,1:02:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the witness observer then
Dialogue: 0,1:02:29.00,1:02:31.00,Default,,0,0,0,,is
Dialogue: 0,1:02:31.00,1:02:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,a higher state
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.00,1:02:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,because the ego is not making
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.00,1:02:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,conclusions, judgments
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.00,1:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't want to control anything
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.00,1:02:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,it merely wants to witness
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.00,1:02:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:02:43.23,1:02:45.23,Default,,0,0,0,,when you go out of body
Dialogue: 0,1:02:45.23,1:02:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,at least
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.23,1:02:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,one out of body
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.23,1:02:51.23,Default,,0,0,0,,there was only the witness observer there
Dialogue: 0,1:02:51.23,1:02:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't have any particular
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.23,1:02:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,intention about anything
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.23,1:02:57.23,Default,,0,0,0,,it was just aware
Dialogue: 0,1:02:57.23,1:02:59.61,Default,,0,0,0,,of it
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.61,1:03:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,like people who leave the body
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.61,1:03:03.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in surgery and go up to the ceiling
Dialogue: 0,1:03:03.61,1:03:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,and witness the surgery
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.61,1:03:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,the witness observer
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.76,1:03:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't want to do anything
Dialogue: 0,1:03:09.90,1:03:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,but watches everything
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.90,1:03:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,just watches
Dialogue: 0,1:03:13.90,1:03:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,say what did you do when you were up near the ceiling
Dialogue: 0,1:03:15.90,1:03:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,didn't do anything but I was aware
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.90,1:03:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,of what was going on
Dialogue: 0,1:03:19.90,1:03:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,be the witness observer
Dialogue: 0,1:03:22.11,1:03:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,that's a state you can achieve
Dialogue: 0,1:03:24.11,1:03:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,by constant surrender
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.11,1:03:28.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and by
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.38,1:03:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,contemplation
Dialogue: 0,1:03:30.38,1:03:32.69,Default,,0,0,0,,the contemplative state
Dialogue: 0,1:03:32.69,1:03:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,puts you in the witness observer
Dialogue: 0,1:03:34.69,1:03:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,puts you in the witness observer
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.21,1:03:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,practice meditation
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.92,1:03:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and contemplation
Dialogue: 0,1:03:41.92,1:03:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,as you do that
Dialogue: 0,1:03:44.26,1:03:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,the witness observer
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.26,1:03:48.26,Default,,0,0,0,,becomes predominant
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.26,1:03:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and becomes
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.30,1:03:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,more or less one's normal state
Dialogue: 0,1:03:52.30,1:03:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:03:54.59,1:03:57.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the only trouble with that is
Dialogue: 0,1:03:57.51,1:03:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you're asking people questions all the time
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.51,1:04:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,what day is it
Dialogue: 0,1:04:01.63,1:04:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,differentiate wants from needs
Dialogue: 0,1:04:03.63,1:04:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,what you want
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.73,1:04:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,is one thing and what you need is another
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.73,1:04:09.90,Default,,0,0,0,,people convince themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:04:09.90,1:04:11.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that their wants are their needs
Dialogue: 0,1:04:11.90,1:04:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,they always have to have a raise
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.90,1:04:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody has to have more money
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.90,1:04:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,that's universal
Dialogue: 0,1:04:17.90,1:04:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter how much you make
Dialogue: 0,1:04:19.96,1:04:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,you need more money
Dialogue: 0,1:04:22.51,1:04:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,if you ask any multi-billionaire
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.51,1:04:26.51,Default,,0,0,0,,what's your problem
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.51,1:04:28.51,Default,,0,0,0,,he says well I just need more
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.51,1:04:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,capital
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.51,1:04:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I could buy the whole United States
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.51,1:04:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of just the eastern seaboard
Dialogue: 0,1:04:34.51,1:04:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.98,1:04:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and Jesus Christ said
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.98,1:04:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,wear the world like a light garment
Dialogue: 0,1:04:41.98,1:04:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,in other words
Dialogue: 0,1:04:43.98,1:04:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,participate
Dialogue: 0,1:04:46.30,1:04:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,see that it's there
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.30,1:04:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,but it's not central
Dialogue: 0,1:04:50.30,1:04:52.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego is not central
Dialogue: 0,1:04:52.30,1:04:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,wear the world like a light garment
Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.46,1:04:56.46,Default,,0,0,0,,so you're the witness observer
Dialogue: 0,1:04:56.46,1:04:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,you observe the world
Dialogue: 0,1:04:58.67,1:05:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and differentiate appearance from essence
Dialogue: 0,1:05:00.67,1:05:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,that's what
Dialogue: 0,1:05:02.88,1:05:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,we do when we use the arm
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.88,1:05:07.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to calibrate something
Dialogue: 0,1:05:07.03,1:05:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the appearance of a thing is one thing
Dialogue: 0,1:05:09.03,1:05:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the essence is another
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.07,1:05:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego cannot tell
Dialogue: 0,1:05:13.07,1:05:15.09,Default,,0,0,0,,essence from appearance
Dialogue: 0,1:05:15.09,1:05:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it just sees the wolf in sheep's clothing
Dialogue: 0,1:05:17.09,1:05:19.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.23,1:05:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,sheep in wolf's clothing
Dialogue: 0,1:05:21.23,1:05:23.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the wolf in sheep's clothing
Dialogue: 0,1:05:23.38,1:05:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,differentiate appearance from essence
Dialogue: 0,1:05:25.38,1:05:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,be kind to all of life
Dialogue: 0,1:05:28.96,1:05:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,why
Dialogue: 0,1:05:30.96,1:05:33.11,Default,,0,0,0,,for its own sake
Dialogue: 0,1:05:33.11,1:05:35.11,Default,,0,0,0,,because of your own reverence for life
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.11,1:05:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,because of your own reverence for life
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.30,1:05:39.46,Default,,0,0,0,,you try to be kind
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.46,1:05:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,to all of life
Dialogue: 0,1:05:41.46,1:05:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,in all of its expressions
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.46,1:05:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,no matter whether it's a toad
Dialogue: 0,1:05:45.46,1:05:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,or a bunny or a squirrel
Dialogue: 0,1:05:47.46,1:05:49.46,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it's another human being
Dialogue: 0,1:05:49.46,1:05:51.63,Default,,0,0,0,,whether it's a tree
Dialogue: 0,1:05:51.63,1:05:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I never hurt a tree
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.63,1:05:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I try to be kind to trees
Dialogue: 0,1:05:55.63,1:05:57.69,Default,,0,0,0,,you see some people take an axe
Dialogue: 0,1:05:57.69,1:05:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,a hand axe
Dialogue: 0,1:05:59.69,1:06:01.69,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're going by a tree
Dialogue: 0,1:06:01.69,1:06:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,they slam it into the tree
Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.69,1:06:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,and then walk on
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.88,1:06:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,pull it out and walk on
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.88,1:06:10.11,Default,,0,0,0,,what do you think the tree didn't know
Dialogue: 0,1:06:10.11,1:06:12.11,Default,,0,0,0,,you just hit it with an axe
Dialogue: 0,1:06:12.11,1:06:14.11,Default,,0,0,0,,if you ask the tree
Dialogue: 0,1:06:14.11,1:06:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,how was that
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.11,1:06:19.42,Default,,0,0,0,,the tree will go
Dialogue: 0,1:06:19.42,1:06:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,all of life then
Dialogue: 0,1:06:21.42,1:06:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,is aware of the nature
Dialogue: 0,1:06:23.42,1:06:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,of the other life
Dialogue: 0,1:06:25.80,1:06:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,in an advanced state of consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:27.80,1:06:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,you'll see
Dialogue: 0,1:06:30.25,1:06:32.25,Default,,0,0,0,,that the tree
Dialogue: 0,1:06:32.25,1:06:34.25,Default,,0,0,0,,is aware of the divinity of yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:06:34.25,1:06:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,the self with a capital s
Dialogue: 0,1:06:36.25,1:06:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,as you walk by a tree
Dialogue: 0,1:06:39.01,1:06:41.01,Default,,0,0,0,,its consciousness
Dialogue: 0,1:06:41.01,1:06:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,which any scientist
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.07,1:06:45.40,Default,,0,0,0,,would poo poo
Dialogue: 0,1:06:45.40,1:06:47.40,Default,,0,0,0,,is aware of the divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:06:47.40,1:06:49.40,Default,,0,0,0,,of that which is walking by
Dialogue: 0,1:06:49.40,1:06:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that's true
Dialogue: 0,1:06:51.98,1:06:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,that's true
Dialogue: 0,1:06:53.98,1:06:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,even a tree
Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.98,1:06:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,is aware of the divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:06:57.98,1:07:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the godness within you
Dialogue: 0,1:07:00.17,1:07:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,the tree is aware
Dialogue: 0,1:07:02.78,1:07:04.78,Default,,0,0,0,,that an emissary of god
Dialogue: 0,1:07:04.78,1:07:07.26,Default,,0,0,0,,is walking by
Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.26,1:07:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,let's try it again
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.36,1:07:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,even a tree is aware
Dialogue: 0,1:07:11.36,1:07:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,that you are an emissary of god
Dialogue: 0,1:07:13.76,1:07:16.34,Default,,0,0,0,,even a tree is aware
Dialogue: 0,1:07:16.34,1:07:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,all of nature
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.34,1:07:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,knows
Dialogue: 0,1:07:22.30,1:07:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,that that which is of divine origin
Dialogue: 0,1:07:24.30,1:07:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is walking by
Dialogue: 0,1:07:26.30,1:07:29.57,Default,,0,0,0,,all the more reason
Dialogue: 0,1:07:29.57,1:07:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,to be kind to it
Dialogue: 0,1:07:32.03,1:07:34.05,Default,,0,0,0,,if consciousness expresses life
Dialogue: 0,1:07:34.05,1:07:36.05,Default,,0,0,0,,is aware of the divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:07:36.05,1:07:38.11,Default,,0,0,0,,of your essence
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.11,1:07:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,out of respect for that life
Dialogue: 0,1:07:40.53,1:07:42.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you return the favor
Dialogue: 0,1:07:42.53,1:07:44.53,Default,,0,0,0,,and therefore
Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.53,1:07:46.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the trees
Dialogue: 0,1:07:46.53,1:07:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I love the kitties
Dialogue: 0,1:07:48.53,1:07:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,I love all living things
Dialogue: 0,1:07:50.53,1:07:52.53,Default,,0,0,0,,because their essence
Dialogue: 0,1:07:52.53,1:07:54.59,Default,,0,0,0,,is also that of divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:07:54.59,1:07:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,this is god appearing as a kitty cat
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.59,1:07:58.59,Default,,0,0,0,,this is god appearing as a mole
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.59,1:08:01.30,Default,,0,0,0,,this is god appearing as a toad
Dialogue: 0,1:08:01.30,1:08:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you see the little toad
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.03,1:08:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,don't you see
Dialogue: 0,1:08:11.84,1:08:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,the toad loves life
Dialogue: 0,1:08:14.38,1:08:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,he loves
Dialogue: 0,1:08:17.14,1:08:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,like a toad
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.07,1:08:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,so to take a hammer
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.84,1:08:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and hit the toad
Dialogue: 0,1:08:24.84,1:08:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,as you can see
Dialogue: 0,1:08:27.22,1:08:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the extreme ungodliness of that
Dialogue: 0,1:08:30.53,1:08:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,because that is denying
Dialogue: 0,1:08:32.53,1:08:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,the divinity
Dialogue: 0,1:08:34.53,1:08:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,of all that exists
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.53,1:08:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,all that exists
Dialogue: 0,1:08:38.85,1:08:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is worthy of reverence
Dialogue: 0,1:08:40.85,1:08:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,so as we grow
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.85,1:08:44.85,Default,,0,0,0,,we begin to revere
Dialogue: 0,1:08:44.85,1:08:47.36,Default,,0,0,0,,all of life
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.36,1:08:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of its expressions
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.36,1:08:51.52,Default,,0,0,0,,even the mad dog
Dialogue: 0,1:08:51.52,1:08:53.52,Default,,0,0,0,,even the raving maniac
Dialogue: 0,1:08:53.52,1:08:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,who can't help but be a raving maniac
Dialogue: 0,1:08:55.94,1:08:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,they cannot help themselves
Dialogue: 0,1:08:57.94,1:09:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,so out of benevolence
Dialogue: 0,1:09:00.17,1:09:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,then
Dialogue: 0,1:09:02.56,1:09:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you send unconditional love
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.06,1:09:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,to all of life
Dialogue: 0,1:09:07.06,1:09:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and wish it well
Dialogue: 0,1:09:11.07,1:09:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,differentiate appearance from essence
Dialogue: 0,1:09:13.07,1:09:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,be kind to all of life
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.47,1:09:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:09:17.47,1:09:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,so you can practice with this
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.65,1:09:21.65,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very beneficial
Dialogue: 0,1:09:21.65,1:09:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,to have pets
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.65,1:09:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and a garden spot
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.85,1:09:27.85,Default,,0,0,0,,the pet could be anything
Dialogue: 0,1:09:27.85,1:09:30.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the pet could be cockroaches
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.07,1:09:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,in a little box
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.61,1:09:34.61,Default,,0,0,0,,the pet could be anything
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.61,1:09:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,my mother used to make me let them go
Dialogue: 0,1:09:36.61,1:09:38.61,Default,,0,0,0,,don't keep them in the box
Dialogue: 0,1:09:38.61,1:09:41.19,Default,,0,0,0,,those are cockroaches
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.19,1:09:43.19,Default,,0,0,0,,alright
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.19,1:09:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,decrease your expectations of others
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.02,1:09:48.02,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody is going to ever reach
Dialogue: 0,1:09:48.02,1:09:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the level
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.02,1:09:52.80,Default,,0,0,0,,at which you would wish them
Dialogue: 0,1:09:52.80,1:09:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so
Dialogue: 0,1:09:54.80,1:09:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the expectation has to be
Dialogue: 0,1:09:56.80,1:09:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can see
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.80,1:10:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,that everybody has been programmed
Dialogue: 0,1:10:00.80,1:10:02.80,Default,,0,0,0,,by our society
Dialogue: 0,1:10:02.80,1:10:04.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so few are the people
Dialogue: 0,1:10:04.80,1:10:06.80,Default,,0,0,0,,who escape the programming
Dialogue: 0,1:10:06.80,1:10:09.34,Default,,0,0,0,,of our human world
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.34,1:10:11.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it's very good
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.60,1:10:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,for your peace of mind
Dialogue: 0,1:10:13.60,1:10:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,to mind your own business
Dialogue: 0,1:10:17.81,1:10:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,mind your own business
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.81,1:10:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,mind your own business
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.89,1:10:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,oh dear
Dialogue: 0,1:10:25.93,1:10:28.09,Default,,0,0,0,,make a list of your worries
Dialogue: 0,1:10:28.09,1:10:30.09,Default,,0,0,0,,oh dear
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.09,1:10:32.09,Default,,0,0,0,,if you can't get rid of your worries
Dialogue: 0,1:10:32.09,1:10:34.09,Default,,0,0,0,,it's important to make a list of them
Dialogue: 0,1:10:34.09,1:10:36.69,Default,,0,0,0,,has everybody here got any worries
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.69,1:10:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,anybody here
Dialogue: 0,1:10:38.69,1:10:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,who doesn't have any worries
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.69,1:10:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,alright the mental ward is that way
Dialogue: 0,1:10:49.42,1:10:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,one way to get on top of your worries
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.06,1:10:54.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is to make a list of them
Dialogue: 0,1:10:54.06,1:10:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and prioritize them
Dialogue: 0,1:10:56.35,1:10:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,because when you identify them
Dialogue: 0,1:10:58.35,1:11:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,you can deal with them
Dialogue: 0,1:11:00.35,1:11:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,otherwise they're just sort of
Dialogue: 0,1:11:02.35,1:11:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,a vague, vague thing
Dialogue: 0,1:11:04.35,1:11:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,worrying about money, worrying about old age
Dialogue: 0,1:11:06.35,1:11:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,worrying about
Dialogue: 0,1:11:08.56,1:11:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,your business collapsing, whatever it is
Dialogue: 0,1:11:10.56,1:11:12.67,Default,,0,0,0,,if you sit down
Dialogue: 0,1:11:12.67,1:11:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,and make a list of worries
Dialogue: 0,1:11:14.67,1:11:16.67,Default,,0,0,0,,they lose a good deal of power
Dialogue: 0,1:11:16.67,1:11:18.80,Default,,0,0,0,,over you
Dialogue: 0,1:11:18.80,1:11:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,because you're defining them
Dialogue: 0,1:11:20.80,1:11:22.80,Default,,0,0,0,,when you define them
Dialogue: 0,1:11:22.80,1:11:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you confine them
Dialogue: 0,1:11:24.80,1:11:27.21,Default,,0,0,0,,and you see how small they actually are
Dialogue: 0,1:11:27.21,1:11:29.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean if you go flat broke
Dialogue: 0,1:11:29.21,1:11:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you go into county
Dialogue: 0,1:11:32.39,1:11:34.39,Default,,0,0,0,,so what's wrong with being in the county
Dialogue: 0,1:11:34.39,1:11:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,you're flat broke
Dialogue: 0,1:11:36.39,1:11:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,got no money, no place to go
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.10,1:11:41.10,Default,,0,0,0,,what better place to be
Dialogue: 0,1:11:41.10,1:11:44.40,Default,,0,0,0,,chocolate versus vanilla
Dialogue: 0,1:11:44.40,1:11:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,is simply a choice
Dialogue: 0,1:11:47.18,1:11:49.18,Default,,0,0,0,,alright what the world does
Dialogue: 0,1:11:49.18,1:11:51.27,Default,,0,0,0,,it says
Dialogue: 0,1:11:51.27,1:11:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,the people on this side are chocolate
Dialogue: 0,1:11:53.27,1:11:55.27,Default,,0,0,0,,and the people on this side are vanilla
Dialogue: 0,1:11:55.27,1:11:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:11:58.30,1:12:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,they don't have to be seen
Dialogue: 0,1:12:00.30,1:12:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,as adversaries
Dialogue: 0,1:12:02.43,1:12:06.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see
Dialogue: 0,1:12:06.47,1:12:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,you can choose chocolate
Dialogue: 0,1:12:08.47,1:12:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,doesn't mean you have to
Dialogue: 0,1:12:10.47,1:12:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,hate vanilla
Dialogue: 0,1:12:12.82,1:12:14.82,Default,,0,0,0,,you can choose vanilla doesn't mean
Dialogue: 0,1:12:14.82,1:12:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you have to hate chocolate
Dialogue: 0,1:12:17.14,1:12:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,if you watch the political news
Dialogue: 0,1:12:19.14,1:12:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,you would think the only way you can be vanilla
Dialogue: 0,1:12:21.14,1:12:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,is you gotta hate chocolate or vice versa
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.60,1:12:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,actually you're just picking
Dialogue: 0,1:12:25.60,1:12:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,one of two choices
Dialogue: 0,1:12:28.19,1:12:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,differentiate your emotional
Dialogue: 0,1:12:30.19,1:12:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,from your spiritual viewpoints
Dialogue: 0,1:12:32.48,1:12:34.48,Default,,0,0,0,,people will use an excuse
Dialogue: 0,1:12:34.48,1:12:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,well I feel this way
Dialogue: 0,1:12:36.90,1:12:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,they use the emotional
Dialogue: 0,1:12:43.52,1:12:45.84,Default,,0,0,0,,outlet
Dialogue: 0,1:12:45.84,1:12:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,why did you do that
Dialogue: 0,1:12:47.84,1:12:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,well I felt like that
Dialogue: 0,1:12:49.84,1:12:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the big excuse
Dialogue: 0,1:12:51.84,1:12:53.84,Default,,0,0,0,,what was your emotional viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,1:12:53.84,1:12:55.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and what was your spiritual viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,1:12:55.84,1:12:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,well my spiritual viewpoint
Dialogue: 0,1:12:57.84,1:12:59.84,Default,,0,0,0,,is somewhat different
Dialogue: 0,1:12:59.84,1:13:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so you don't want to be the slave
Dialogue: 0,1:13:01.89,1:13:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,of the ego and its emotions
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.89,1:13:05.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and don't forget that the ego
Dialogue: 0,1:13:05.89,1:13:07.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the basis of the mind
Dialogue: 0,1:13:07.89,1:13:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,is the child
Dialogue: 0,1:13:09.89,1:13:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,so when you're talking about emotions
Dialogue: 0,1:13:11.89,1:13:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,very often you're talking about
Dialogue: 0,1:13:13.89,1:13:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the inner child
Dialogue: 0,1:13:15.89,1:13:18.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and not the inner adult
Dialogue: 0,1:13:18.43,1:13:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and in fighting your way out of
Dialogue: 0,1:13:20.51,1:13:22.51,Default,,0,0,0,,some corner
Dialogue: 0,1:13:22.51,1:13:24.51,Default,,0,0,0,,the emotional corner
Dialogue: 0,1:13:24.51,1:13:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,use logic instead of emotion
Dialogue: 0,1:13:26.53,1:13:28.53,Default,,0,0,0,,a lot of people try emotion
Dialogue: 0,1:13:28.53,1:13:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,instead of just logic
Dialogue: 0,1:13:30.53,1:13:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,if you use logic
Dialogue: 0,1:13:32.53,1:13:34.53,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see there's nothing to be afraid of
Dialogue: 0,1:13:34.53,1:13:36.53,Default,,0,0,0,,when life is over
Dialogue: 0,1:13:36.53,1:13:38.53,Default,,0,0,0,,they bury you and that's the end of the problem
Dialogue: 0,1:13:38.53,1:13:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,so what's the problem
Dialogue: 0,1:13:43.68,1:13:46.03,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's over it's over
Dialogue: 0,1:13:46.03,1:13:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,no more suffering
Dialogue: 0,1:13:48.81,1:13:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,ask for a miracle
Dialogue: 0,1:13:50.97,1:13:52.97,Default,,0,0,0,,those of you who have done the course of miracles
Dialogue: 0,1:13:52.97,1:13:54.97,Default,,0,0,0,,know that this
Dialogue: 0,1:13:54.97,1:13:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,in itself is a miracle
Dialogue: 0,1:13:56.97,1:13:58.97,Default,,0,0,0,,that asking for a miracle
Dialogue: 0,1:13:58.97,1:14:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,very often
Dialogue: 0,1:14:01.44,1:14:03.64,Default,,0,0,0,,produces the miracle
Dialogue: 0,1:14:03.64,1:14:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot find the thing
Dialogue: 0,1:14:05.64,1:14:07.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no idea where it is
Dialogue: 0,1:14:07.64,1:14:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a complete blank
Dialogue: 0,1:14:09.64,1:14:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'll ask the Holy Spirit
Dialogue: 0,1:14:11.64,1:14:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,where is so and so
Dialogue: 0,1:14:13.64,1:14:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and then I forget it
Dialogue: 0,1:14:15.89,1:14:17.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I walk in the other room
Dialogue: 0,1:14:17.89,1:14:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,and then out of nowhere
Dialogue: 0,1:14:19.89,1:14:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,not out of logic
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.89,1:14:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,out of nowhere
Dialogue: 0,1:14:23.89,1:14:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,it comes to my mind you're left in the bathroom on the shelf
Dialogue: 0,1:14:25.89,1:14:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got it
Dialogue: 0,1:14:27.89,1:14:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,everything I ever lose is in the bathroom
Dialogue: 0,1:14:29.89,1:14:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,in the shelf
Dialogue: 0,1:14:31.89,1:14:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,or the kitchen on the shelf
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.67,1:14:39.39,Default,,0,0,0,,ask for a miracle
Dialogue: 0,1:14:39.39,1:14:41.39,Default,,0,0,0,,people feel they're not entitled to miracles
Dialogue: 0,1:14:41.39,1:14:43.39,Default,,0,0,0,,or that they don't believe it
Dialogue: 0,1:14:43.39,1:14:45.39,Default,,0,0,0,,people don't know what a miracle is
Dialogue: 0,1:14:45.39,1:14:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,very often a miracle is
Dialogue: 0,1:14:47.39,1:14:49.39,Default,,0,0,0,,merely the reframing
Dialogue: 0,1:14:49.39,1:14:51.39,Default,,0,0,0,,the thing has been reframed
Dialogue: 0,1:14:51.39,1:14:53.78,Default,,0,0,0,,especially in time
Dialogue: 0,1:14:53.78,1:14:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,it wasn't expected in time
Dialogue: 0,1:14:56.03,1:14:58.03,Default,,0,0,0,,today is tomorrow as yesterday
Dialogue: 0,1:14:58.03,1:15:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,today
Dialogue: 0,1:15:00.23,1:15:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,is tomorrow as yesterday
Dialogue: 0,1:15:02.39,1:15:04.39,Default,,0,0,0,,good God it's yesterday already
Dialogue: 0,1:15:04.39,1:15:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and here I'm worrying about it
Dialogue: 0,1:15:08.22,1:15:12.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I was worrying about getting back here on time
Dialogue: 0,1:15:12.23,1:15:14.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:15:14.23,1:15:16.23,Default,,0,0,0,,that's going to be yesterday
Dialogue: 0,1:15:16.23,1:15:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,today's going to be yesterday
Dialogue: 0,1:15:18.52,1:15:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and we'll say we were worried about getting back on time
Dialogue: 0,1:15:20.52,1:15:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,yesterday
Dialogue: 0,1:15:24.61,1:15:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,aside from having a mentor
Dialogue: 0,1:15:27.31,1:15:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,talking things over with friends
Dialogue: 0,1:15:29.31,1:15:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is really
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.31,1:15:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,very important
Dialogue: 0,1:15:33.31,1:15:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,because an isolated person
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.31,1:15:37.44,Default,,0,0,0,,ends up pretty crazy
Dialogue: 0,1:15:37.44,1:15:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and who was it
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.15,1:15:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,whatchamacallit
Dialogue: 0,1:15:42.15,1:15:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,a killer
Dialogue: 0,1:15:44.31,1:15:46.31,Default,,0,0,0,,lived by himself in an 8x10
Dialogue: 0,1:15:46.31,1:15:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,terrified all of industry
Dialogue: 0,1:15:48.43,1:15:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,and all
Dialogue: 0,1:15:50.43,1:15:53.11,Default,,0,0,0,,he didn't have any friends to talk it over with
Dialogue: 0,1:15:53.11,1:15:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I forget his name now
Dialogue: 0,1:15:58.02,1:16:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,huh
Dialogue: 0,1:16:02.81,1:16:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,the unibomber
Dialogue: 0,1:16:05.13,1:16:07.13,Default,,0,0,0,,that's it
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.13,1:16:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,the unibomber had nobody to talk it over with
Dialogue: 0,1:16:10.00,1:16:12.00,Default,,0,0,0,,if he talked it over with friends
Dialogue: 0,1:16:12.00,1:16:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,he might have been dissuaded
Dialogue: 0,1:16:15.78,1:16:20.67,Default,,0,0,0,,he might have been dissuaded
Dialogue: 0,1:16:20.67,1:16:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,now
Dialogue: 0,1:16:22.67,1:16:24.67,Default,,0,0,0,,he wanted to be all by himself
Dialogue: 0,1:16:24.67,1:16:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,in an 8x10
Dialogue: 0,1:16:27.27,1:16:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,space
Dialogue: 0,1:16:29.76,1:16:31.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand he is now all by himself
Dialogue: 0,1:16:31.76,1:16:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,in a 10x12 space
Dialogue: 0,1:16:33.76,1:16:37.06,Default,,0,0,0,,he probably feels
Dialogue: 0,1:16:37.06,1:16:39.06,Default,,0,0,0,,he's rattling around in that big cell
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.06,1:16:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,as you can see
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.30,1:16:46.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the person with schizophrenia
Dialogue: 0,1:16:46.30,1:16:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,and delusions
Dialogue: 0,1:16:48.30,1:16:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,is unable to help himself
Dialogue: 0,1:16:50.30,1:16:52.56,Default,,0,0,0,,so even though he was
Dialogue: 0,1:16:52.56,1:16:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,the unibomber
Dialogue: 0,1:16:54.68,1:16:56.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't hate him
Dialogue: 0,1:16:56.68,1:16:58.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you can't want to get even with him
Dialogue: 0,1:16:58.68,1:17:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,how can you see the unibomber
Dialogue: 0,1:17:00.68,1:17:02.68,Default,,0,0,0,,except as a person
Dialogue: 0,1:17:02.68,1:17:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,who was spiritually lost
Dialogue: 0,1:17:04.68,1:17:06.90,Default,,0,0,0,,he was spiritually lost
Dialogue: 0,1:17:06.90,1:17:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritually lost
Dialogue: 0,1:17:08.90,1:17:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,spiritually lost
Dialogue: 0,1:17:10.97,1:17:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,completely egocentric
Dialogue: 0,1:17:12.97,1:17:15.28,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:17:15.28,1:17:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,so not having friends to talk it over with
Dialogue: 0,1:17:17.28,1:17:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,another way to
Dialogue: 0,1:17:20.06,1:17:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,down your fears and worries
Dialogue: 0,1:17:22.06,1:17:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,is to accept the worst possible scenario
Dialogue: 0,1:17:24.06,1:17:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,worst possible scenario
Dialogue: 0,1:17:26.80,1:17:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,worst possible scenario
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.80,1:17:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,picture it in your mind
Dialogue: 0,1:17:30.80,1:17:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,well the worst thing that can happen
Dialogue: 0,1:17:32.80,1:17:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,is I get a flat tire on the parkway
Dialogue: 0,1:17:34.80,1:17:36.96,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's raining
Dialogue: 0,1:17:36.96,1:17:39.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and I forgot my drivers license
Dialogue: 0,1:17:39.52,1:17:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,that's the worst possible scenario
Dialogue: 0,1:17:41.52,1:17:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,then you say
Dialogue: 0,1:17:43.94,1:17:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,well now what if all that happened
Dialogue: 0,1:17:46.64,1:17:48.64,Default,,0,0,0,,well I'd catch hell from the cop
Dialogue: 0,1:17:48.64,1:17:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and I'd have to pay the fine
Dialogue: 0,1:17:50.64,1:17:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,that's true
Dialogue: 0,1:17:52.77,1:17:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,well if that's the worst possible scenario
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.77,1:17:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,you don't have to be frightened
Dialogue: 0,1:17:57.06,1:17:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,one time I left Phoenix
Dialogue: 0,1:17:59.06,1:18:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,to go up to
Dialogue: 0,1:18:01.93,1:18:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,where is it we live
Dialogue: 0,1:18:04.27,1:18:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,wherever it is we live
Dialogue: 0,1:18:06.38,1:18:08.38,Default,,0,0,0,,and
Dialogue: 0,1:18:08.38,1:18:10.98,Default,,0,0,0,,it's two hours away
Dialogue: 0,1:18:10.98,1:18:12.98,Default,,0,0,0,,a couple hours north of Phoenix
Dialogue: 0,1:18:12.98,1:18:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and I started to leave Phoenix
Dialogue: 0,1:18:14.98,1:18:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,and my headlights went out
Dialogue: 0,1:18:16.98,1:18:19.50,Default,,0,0,0,,the battery went dead
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.50,1:18:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,so here I am 110 or whatever it is
Dialogue: 0,1:18:21.50,1:18:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,miles
Dialogue: 0,1:18:23.50,1:18:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and it's midnight
Dialogue: 0,1:18:25.56,1:18:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,pitch black out and I've got no headlights
Dialogue: 0,1:18:27.56,1:18:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,well wouldn't do me much good
Dialogue: 0,1:18:30.19,1:18:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to pull over the side of the road
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.32,1:18:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,so what I did is I followed the car
Dialogue: 0,1:18:34.32,1:18:37.28,Default,,0,0,0,,ahead of me
Dialogue: 0,1:18:37.28,1:18:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,and I very carefully did everything he did
Dialogue: 0,1:18:39.28,1:18:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,when he went this way I went that way
Dialogue: 0,1:18:41.89,1:18:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew that sooner or later
Dialogue: 0,1:18:43.89,1:18:45.89,Default,,0,0,0,,the driver is going to see some guy with his lights out
Dialogue: 0,1:18:45.89,1:18:48.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is behind me
Dialogue: 0,1:18:48.85,1:18:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and he will conclude that this guy is following me home
Dialogue: 0,1:18:50.85,1:18:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,because he's got no lights
Dialogue: 0,1:18:53.76,1:18:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,so I followed him for two hours
Dialogue: 0,1:18:55.76,1:18:58.10,Default,,0,0,0,,150 miles
Dialogue: 0,1:18:58.10,1:19:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,or whatever the distance is
Dialogue: 0,1:19:00.10,1:19:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and I was
Dialogue: 0,1:19:02.10,1:19:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,worried that I was frightening the guy
Dialogue: 0,1:19:04.10,1:19:06.10,Default,,0,0,0,,so I asked God
Dialogue: 0,1:19:06.10,1:19:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I said please don't let him be frightened
Dialogue: 0,1:19:08.10,1:19:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I just need him to guide me home
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.32,1:19:12.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and the guy I think
Dialogue: 0,1:19:12.32,1:19:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,he did understand it
Dialogue: 0,1:19:14.32,1:19:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,he eventually did understand it
Dialogue: 0,1:19:16.32,1:19:18.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and he got that I was a man in distress
Dialogue: 0,1:19:18.32,1:19:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and let's
Dialogue: 0,1:19:20.32,1:19:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I have permission to ask this
Dialogue: 0,1:19:22.35,1:19:24.35,Default,,0,0,0,,he finally got it
Dialogue: 0,1:19:24.35,1:19:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah he got it
Dialogue: 0,1:19:26.35,1:19:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I was praying that he would get it
Dialogue: 0,1:19:28.35,1:19:30.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I said dear God please let him just get that
Dialogue: 0,1:19:30.35,1:19:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I got to get up the highway
Dialogue: 0,1:19:32.35,1:19:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,and I got no headlights
Dialogue: 0,1:19:34.75,1:19:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,so that worked out
Dialogue: 0,1:19:36.75,1:19:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,that was the worst possible scenario
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.60,1:19:42.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I like this one
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.38,1:19:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the movie that should have won the best film ever
Dialogue: 0,1:19:44.38,1:19:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Scarlett O'Hara
Dialogue: 0,1:19:47.81,1:19:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,they named some other movie
Dialogue: 0,1:19:49.81,1:19:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't understand why they picked the movie they did
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.81,1:19:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,when obviously
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.81,1:19:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,this is the greatest movie ever made
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.81,1:19:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:19:57.85,1:19:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,and Scarlett would say
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.85,1:20:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think about it tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:20:02.72,1:20:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,well in the modern world
Dialogue: 0,1:20:05.00,1:20:07.00,Default,,0,0,0,,that would be criticized wouldn't it
Dialogue: 0,1:20:07.00,1:20:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,think about it tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:20:09.00,1:20:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,this that and the other
Dialogue: 0,1:20:11.15,1:20:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but there's a certain wisdom to that
Dialogue: 0,1:20:13.15,1:20:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,because if you think about it tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:20:15.15,1:20:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,it doesn't look the same
Dialogue: 0,1:20:17.35,1:20:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,for one thing you start a process
Dialogue: 0,1:20:19.35,1:20:22.40,Default,,0,0,0,,going in your unconscious mind
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.40,1:20:24.40,Default,,0,0,0,,and so when you say
Dialogue: 0,1:20:24.40,1:20:26.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't think of how I'm going to make any money
Dialogue: 0,1:20:26.40,1:20:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I haven't got any assets
Dialogue: 0,1:20:28.40,1:20:30.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've got no income
Dialogue: 0,1:20:30.51,1:20:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and I've been cut off now
Dialogue: 0,1:20:32.51,1:20:34.51,Default,,0,0,0,,and you say well I'll think about it tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:20:34.51,1:20:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll think about it tomorrow
Dialogue: 0,1:20:36.51,1:20:38.51,Default,,0,0,0,,then suddenly
Dialogue: 0,1:20:38.51,1:20:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,in the morning you get up
Dialogue: 0,1:20:40.51,1:20:42.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you're self boiling an egg
Dialogue: 0,1:20:42.56,1:20:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,and all of a sudden
Dialogue: 0,1:20:44.56,1:20:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you remind yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:20:46.80,1:20:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,well I could take this to a hock shop
Dialogue: 0,1:20:48.80,1:20:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and probably get a couple hundred bucks
Dialogue: 0,1:20:50.80,1:20:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,right yesterday you didn't think of that
Dialogue: 0,1:20:52.92,1:20:54.92,Default,,0,0,0,,today it's obvious
Dialogue: 0,1:20:54.92,1:20:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody's got something in your house
Dialogue: 0,1:20:57.43,1:20:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,you can hock
Dialogue: 0,1:20:59.43,1:21:02.07,Default,,0,0,0,,everybody got something you can hock
Dialogue: 0,1:21:02.07,1:21:04.07,Default,,0,0,0,,hockables
Dialogue: 0,1:21:04.07,1:21:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,anybody so poor they haven't even got a hockable
Dialogue: 0,1:21:06.56,1:21:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody's that poor
Dialogue: 0,1:21:08.56,1:21:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,you may have to sleep on the floor
Dialogue: 0,1:21:10.56,1:21:13.15,Default,,0,0,0,,but you've got something to hock
Dialogue: 0,1:21:13.15,1:21:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,there's a new program on that called hock
Dialogue: 0,1:21:15.15,1:21:17.15,Default,,0,0,0,,what is it hock shop or something
Dialogue: 0,1:21:17.15,1:21:19.15,Default,,0,0,0,,about the same night as ice road triggers
Dialogue: 0,1:21:19.15,1:21:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,pawn shop yeah
Dialogue: 0,1:21:25.97,1:21:27.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is peace
Dialogue: 0,1:21:27.97,1:21:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is everywhere
Dialogue: 0,1:21:29.97,1:21:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,existent
Dialogue: 0,1:21:32.32,1:21:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,peace is existent all the time
Dialogue: 0,1:21:34.32,1:21:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,even in the midst of war
Dialogue: 0,1:21:36.48,1:21:38.48,Default,,0,0,0,,even in the midst of war
Dialogue: 0,1:21:38.48,1:21:40.48,Default,,0,0,0,,you know
Dialogue: 0,1:21:40.48,1:21:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,we were about to explode
Dialogue: 0,1:21:42.48,1:21:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,this mine was about to go off
Dialogue: 0,1:21:44.52,1:21:46.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and he says well we might get killed
Dialogue: 0,1:21:46.52,1:21:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and then what happens if we go off
Dialogue: 0,1:21:48.59,1:21:50.59,Default,,0,0,0,,and I said to him well then we die
Dialogue: 0,1:21:50.59,1:21:52.59,Default,,0,0,0,,he said you're right
Dialogue: 0,1:21:52.59,1:21:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,you're right
Dialogue: 0,1:21:54.64,1:21:56.64,Default,,0,0,0,,and his fear went away
Dialogue: 0,1:21:56.64,1:21:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and just the
Dialogue: 0,1:21:59.13,1:22:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,peace in the middle of war
Dialogue: 0,1:22:01.22,1:22:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,there was peace
Dialogue: 0,1:22:03.68,1:22:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in that you were doing exactly
Dialogue: 0,1:22:05.68,1:22:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,what your duty was
Dialogue: 0,1:22:07.68,1:22:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you're supposed to man this particular gun
Dialogue: 0,1:22:09.68,1:22:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you're supposed to watch for strange ships
Dialogue: 0,1:22:11.68,1:22:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,you're supposed to be on guard
Dialogue: 0,1:22:13.68,1:22:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,report anything
Dialogue: 0,1:22:15.68,1:22:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,and so
Dialogue: 0,1:22:17.77,1:22:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,you're standing out there
Dialogue: 0,1:22:19.77,1:22:21.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on a very small ship
Dialogue: 0,1:22:21.77,1:22:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,not one of these big battleships
Dialogue: 0,1:22:23.77,1:22:25.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I was on a minesweeper
Dialogue: 0,1:22:25.80,1:22:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and so we stood watch for four hours
Dialogue: 0,1:22:27.80,1:22:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,at night you see
Dialogue: 0,1:22:29.80,1:22:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you stood watch you wear the gun belt
Dialogue: 0,1:22:31.80,1:22:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,with a loaded 45
Dialogue: 0,1:22:34.00,1:22:36.00,Default,,0,0,0,,loaded 45
Dialogue: 0,1:22:36.00,1:22:38.00,Default,,0,0,0,,and anything that moved you shot it
Dialogue: 0,1:22:40.00,1:22:42.00,Default,,0,0,0,,see something moving over the fantail
Dialogue: 0,1:22:46.40,1:22:48.67,Default,,0,0,0,,anyway things could be worse
Dialogue: 0,1:22:48.67,1:22:50.96,Default,,0,0,0,,life is transitory
Dialogue: 0,1:22:50.96,1:22:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,so that's another thing
Dialogue: 0,1:22:52.96,1:22:54.96,Default,,0,0,0,,the ego thinks that
Dialogue: 0,1:22:54.96,1:22:56.96,Default,,0,0,0,,it's eternal that it's life
Dialogue: 0,1:22:56.96,1:22:59.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is going to be forever
Dialogue: 0,1:22:59.34,1:23:01.34,Default,,0,0,0,,once you accept the fact that life
Dialogue: 0,1:23:01.34,1:23:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,is transitory at best
Dialogue: 0,1:23:03.34,1:23:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,we're all going to go
Dialogue: 0,1:23:05.78,1:23:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,uh oh you didn't expect
Dialogue: 0,1:23:07.78,1:23:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to hear that today
Dialogue: 0,1:23:10.30,1:23:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we're all going to go
Dialogue: 0,1:23:12.30,1:23:14.72,Default,,0,0,0,,anybody thinks they're not
Dialogue: 0,1:23:14.72,1:23:18.22,Default,,0,0,0,,going to go
Dialogue: 0,1:23:18.22,1:23:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,anybody planning not to go
Dialogue: 0,1:23:21.72,1:23:24.61,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:23:24.61,1:23:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,in the infinite
Dialogue: 0,1:23:26.68,1:23:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,dimensions of time
Dialogue: 0,1:23:28.68,1:23:31.31,Default,,0,0,0,,we're all living together
Dialogue: 0,1:23:31.31,1:23:33.31,Default,,0,0,0,,you would think a couple of years here and there
Dialogue: 0,1:23:33.31,1:23:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is different in time
Dialogue: 0,1:23:35.31,1:23:37.39,Default,,0,0,0,,but in compared
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.39,1:23:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,to infinite time
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.44,1:23:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,in the few decades or whatever it is
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.44,1:23:43.44,Default,,0,0,0,,it'll take for all of us to go around the other side
Dialogue: 0,1:23:43.44,1:23:45.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is all about the same time
Dialogue: 0,1:23:45.55,1:23:47.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so frankly we're all going over
Dialogue: 0,1:23:47.55,1:23:50.02,Default,,0,0,0,,about the same time
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.02,1:23:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,some people went ahead and got parking
Dialogue: 0,1:23:52.02,1:23:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,places for us
Dialogue: 0,1:23:54.02,1:23:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:23:56.15,1:23:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,and is over and found us parking places
Dialogue: 0,1:23:58.15,1:24:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,so we get to heaven
Dialogue: 0,1:24:00.35,1:24:02.35,Default,,0,0,0,,we will have parking places
Dialogue: 0,1:24:02.35,1:24:04.35,Default,,0,0,0,,and uh
Dialogue: 0,1:24:04.35,1:24:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,a sign telling us where to go
Dialogue: 0,1:24:06.35,1:24:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.56,1:24:11.94,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:24:11.94,1:24:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,life is transitory
Dialogue: 0,1:24:13.94,1:24:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,the acceptance of that then
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.94,1:24:17.94,Default,,0,0,0,,decreases a great deal of fear
Dialogue: 0,1:24:17.94,1:24:19.94,Default,,0,0,0,,life and all
Dialogue: 0,1:24:19.94,1:24:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,experience of life is transitory
Dialogue: 0,1:24:21.94,1:24:24.30,Default,,0,0,0,,the knowledge that
Dialogue: 0,1:24:24.30,1:24:26.30,Default,,0,0,0,,you were created by God
Dialogue: 0,1:24:26.30,1:24:28.30,Default,,0,0,0,,it then gives us
Dialogue: 0,1:24:28.30,1:24:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,certain solemnity
Dialogue: 0,1:24:30.30,1:24:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,certain profundity
Dialogue: 0,1:24:32.30,1:24:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,lets see if we have permission to ask that
Dialogue: 0,1:24:34.30,1:24:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,we have permission to ask this question
Dialogue: 0,1:24:36.30,1:24:40.15,Default,,0,0,0,,we were all created
Dialogue: 0,1:24:40.15,1:24:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,by God resist
Dialogue: 0,1:24:43.34,1:24:45.34,Default,,0,0,0,,we were created by God
Dialogue: 0,1:24:45.34,1:24:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,wow
Dialogue: 0,1:24:47.47,1:24:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,here you thought it was a sperm and an egg
Dialogue: 0,1:24:49.47,1:24:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:24:52.17,1:24:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,a biologic accident
Dialogue: 0,1:24:55.39,1:25:00.35,Default,,0,0,0,,laughter
Dialogue: 0,1:25:00.35,1:25:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,life is transitory
Dialogue: 0,1:25:02.43,1:25:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,that which you really are
Dialogue: 0,1:25:04.43,1:25:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,was created by God
Dialogue: 0,1:25:07.22,1:25:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,so not the ego but the self
Dialogue: 0,1:25:09.22,1:25:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,with a capital S
Dialogue: 0,1:25:11.22,1:25:13.22,Default,,0,0,0,,is the essence of who you are
Dialogue: 0,1:25:13.22,1:25:15.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and when you leave the body
Dialogue: 0,1:25:15.22,1:25:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,those of you who have left
Dialogue: 0,1:25:17.22,1:25:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the experience of leaving the body
Dialogue: 0,1:25:19.22,1:25:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the witness observer witnesses
Dialogue: 0,1:25:21.22,1:25:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,and observes the body but feels no attraction
Dialogue: 0,1:25:23.22,1:25:25.64,Default,,0,0,0,,to it at all
Dialogue: 0,1:25:25.64,1:25:27.64,Default,,0,0,0,,it seems meaningless
Dialogue: 0,1:25:27.64,1:25:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,boring
Dialogue: 0,1:25:29.93,1:25:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,not even attractive
Dialogue: 0,1:25:31.93,1:25:33.93,Default,,0,0,0,,you would think you're trying to get back in that body
Dialogue: 0,1:25:33.93,1:25:35.93,Default,,0,0,0,,and reactivate it
Dialogue: 0,1:25:35.93,1:25:37.93,Default,,0,0,0,,but strangely enough it just lays there
Dialogue: 0,1:25:37.93,1:25:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,it has no attraction
Dialogue: 0,1:25:40.80,1:25:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,you go on a worry diet
Dialogue: 0,1:25:42.80,1:25:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,we said we were going to make a list of worries
Dialogue: 0,1:25:44.80,1:25:46.80,Default,,0,0,0,,so then you begin to pick off
Dialogue: 0,1:25:46.80,1:25:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,your worry diet
Dialogue: 0,1:25:48.80,1:25:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,the things that you're going to let
Dialogue: 0,1:25:50.80,1:25:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,be willing to let go of
Dialogue: 0,1:25:52.96,1:25:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I will stop worrying about money
Dialogue: 0,1:25:55.63,1:25:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,what's going to happen to you if you don't have any money
Dialogue: 0,1:25:57.63,1:26:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're poor
Dialogue: 0,1:26:00.27,1:26:02.27,Default,,0,0,0,,well I've been poor
Dialogue: 0,1:26:02.27,1:26:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're poor there's lots of things you can't have
Dialogue: 0,1:26:04.27,1:26:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,can't have a new Cadillac
Dialogue: 0,1:26:07.55,1:26:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,so you go on a diet
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.55,1:26:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,and you start letting things go
Dialogue: 0,1:26:11.73,1:26:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,could I be happy without a new Cadillac
Dialogue: 0,1:26:13.73,1:26:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,yep
Dialogue: 0,1:26:16.47,1:26:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,could I be happy
Dialogue: 0,1:26:19.05,1:26:21.05,Default,,0,0,0,,if I didn't have a new pair of shoes
Dialogue: 0,1:26:21.05,1:26:23.36,Default,,0,0,0,,yep
Dialogue: 0,1:26:23.36,1:26:25.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got them on so I know
Dialogue: 0,1:26:27.60,1:26:29.60,Default,,0,0,0,,give up on a worry diet
Dialogue: 0,1:26:29.60,1:26:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,give up trying to be happy
Dialogue: 0,1:26:31.63,1:26:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,just
Dialogue: 0,1:26:34.03,1:26:36.03,Default,,0,0,0,,you have an ongoing acceptance
Dialogue: 0,1:26:36.03,1:26:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,now this acceptance
Dialogue: 0,1:26:38.03,1:26:40.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is not the human will
Dialogue: 0,1:26:40.03,1:26:42.19,Default,,0,0,0,,this acceptance
Dialogue: 0,1:26:42.19,1:26:44.19,Default,,0,0,0,,is being the
Dialogue: 0,1:26:44.19,1:26:46.19,Default,,0,0,0,,witness observer
Dialogue: 0,1:26:46.19,1:26:48.19,Default,,0,0,0,,it's a contemplative position
Dialogue: 0,1:26:48.19,1:26:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,not meditative but contemplative
Dialogue: 0,1:26:50.19,1:26:52.27,Default,,0,0,0,,so that as we walk
Dialogue: 0,1:26:52.27,1:26:54.27,Default,,0,0,0,,through the day today
Dialogue: 0,1:26:54.27,1:26:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the stage
Dialogue: 0,1:26:56.52,1:26:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,is here where it is
Dialogue: 0,1:26:58.52,1:27:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,the flowers are where they are
Dialogue: 0,1:27:00.52,1:27:02.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Susan is sitting there
Dialogue: 0,1:27:02.88,1:27:05.19,Default,,0,0,0,,doing fine
Dialogue: 0,1:27:05.19,1:27:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,there's some mysterious person
Dialogue: 0,1:27:07.19,1:27:10.22,Default,,0,0,0,,in the dark over there
Dialogue: 0,1:27:10.22,1:27:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to know who that mysterious
Dialogue: 0,1:27:12.22,1:27:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,person is
Dialogue: 0,1:27:14.35,1:27:16.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I said well I can
Dialogue: 0,1:27:16.98,1:27:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,just control my curiosity
Dialogue: 0,1:27:18.98,1:27:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,do I have to know who's sitting there
Dialogue: 0,1:27:20.98,1:27:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,in the dark
Dialogue: 0,1:27:23.23,1:27:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,no don't have to
Dialogue: 0,1:27:25.85,1:27:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,do I know who's sitting there
Dialogue: 0,1:27:28.72,1:27:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,no
Dialogue: 0,1:27:31.03,1:27:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I presume it's a friend
Dialogue: 0,1:27:33.03,1:27:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,well if it's not a friend
Dialogue: 0,1:27:37.76,1:27:40.93,Default,,0,0,0,,it could be an enemy
Dialogue: 0,1:27:40.93,1:27:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's an enemy
Dialogue: 0,1:27:42.93,1:27:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it could kill you right now
Dialogue: 0,1:27:46.85,1:28:01.07,Default,,0,0,0,,so here I am
Dialogue: 0,1:28:01.07,1:28:04.03,Default,,0,0,0,,do you want to kill me
Dialogue: 0,1:28:04.03,1:28:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,kill me
Dialogue: 0,1:28:07.84,1:28:13.84,Default,,0,0,0,,nobody killed me oh well
Dialogue: 0,1:28:13.84,1:28:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,and you can let go of your worries
Dialogue: 0,1:28:15.84,1:28:17.84,Default,,0,0,0,,if you're motivated
Dialogue: 0,1:28:17.84,1:28:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,by God
Dialogue: 0,1:28:19.84,1:28:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,you can let go of your worries
Dialogue: 0,1:28:21.89,1:28:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,one by one
Dialogue: 0,1:28:23.93,1:28:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,by total acceptance
Dialogue: 0,1:28:25.93,1:28:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,give up trying to be happy
Dialogue: 0,1:28:28.18,1:28:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,don't try to be happy
Dialogue: 0,1:28:30.18,1:28:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,just be happy
Dialogue: 0,1:28:32.18,1:28:34.27,Default,,0,0,0,,don't try to be happy
Dialogue: 0,1:28:34.27,1:28:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,just be happy
Dialogue: 0,1:28:36.27,1:28:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,that's simpler than trying to be happy
Dialogue: 0,1:28:39.63,1:28:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,you can see that trying to be happy
Dialogue: 0,1:28:41.78,1:28:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,is like a mouse chasing its tail
Dialogue: 0,1:28:44.35,1:28:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,stop trying to be happy
Dialogue: 0,1:28:46.35,1:28:54.36,Default,,0,0,0,,should be happy because you are. You are. Fantastic. From nothingness to somethingness,
Dialogue: 0,1:28:55.81,1:29:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,give up trying to be happy. Give up being rich and famous. Oh, everybody's dream in America.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:03.23,1:29:11.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't go to Hollywood and get on the television interview shows. Give up being rich and famous.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:13.43,1:29:16.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You see what happens to the most rich and famous people.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:16.11,1:29:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's rather grisly when you study the truth of their life, their life stories.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:24.77,1:29:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up being rich and famous. What people do to be rich and famous. Have 18 children at once. God
Dialogue: 0,1:29:31.72,1:29:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,knows what people will do. Walk the tightrope over stretches. Who was that great gymnast that
Dialogue: 0,1:29:41.47,1:29:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,finally fell to his death? Famous circus family.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:48.77,1:29:48.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:49.00,1:29:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Italian name. He was the greatest in the world. And he fell to his death anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:29:55.26,1:30:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,So being rich and famous eggs you on to the edge. People with any sense, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:30:02.34,1:30:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,stand back a little. You see, every year about nine people fall over the edge of the Grand Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:08.63,1:30:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,How do they manage that? I'm scared to get within 20 feet of the edge of the Grand Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:22.72,1:30:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I've gotten better. I used to be 50 feet from the edge of the Grand Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:26.48,1:30:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Now I've gotten, I'm up to 20 feet within the Grand Canyon. How do they get over there
Dialogue: 0,1:30:33.67,1:30:42.88,Default,,0,0,0,,where they fall off? Every year about nine people fall into the Grand Canyon. Anybody
Dialogue: 0,1:30:42.88,1:30:49.02,Default,,0,0,0,,who's dumb enough to fall in the Grand Canyon deserves falling in the Grand Canyon.
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.02,1:30:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I think they actually, they're just daredevils. You know, these people that want to parachute
Dialogue: 0,1:30:53.96,1:30:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,out of strange things at strange heights with both legs bound together and a gag in their
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.69,1:31:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,mouth or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:01.86,1:31:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It's what I call vainglorious. What a lot of people think is heroics is nothing but
Dialogue: 0,1:31:11.27,1:31:18.63,Default,,0,0,0,,vainglory. They want to be on the headlines. They jumped all the way from, you know, 30,000
Dialogue: 0,1:31:18.63,1:31:24.59,Default,,0,0,0,,feet and didn't open their parachute until they got to 600 feet down here. So they must
Dialogue: 0,1:31:24.59,1:31:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,have had an exciting ride. Anyway, more spiritual ways are to walk the labyrinth. And you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:33.60,1:31:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,walking the labyrinth,
Dialogue: 0,1:31:34.81,1:31:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,what cathedral was that, Ernie? What cathedral was that? The labyrinth, chart. Anyway, walking
Dialogue: 0,1:31:45.11,1:31:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,the labyrinth, which is very famous. Our church back home has a copy of the labyrinth in the
Dialogue: 0,1:31:50.19,1:31:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,parking lot. The effect of walking the labyrinth is the same if you trace it with a pencil.
Dialogue: 0,1:31:58.55,1:32:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,If you have a diagram of the labyrinth and you take a pencil point, you start from the
Dialogue: 0,1:32:03.98,1:32:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,starting point and you do with the pencil point, you follow the labyrinth where it goes.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:09.55,1:32:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The effect on your consciousness is the same as if you walked it. Isn't that strange? Okay,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:18.64,1:32:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,that's mystical. That is a mystical truth. Nobody knows the reason for it. Nobody knows
Dialogue: 0,1:32:33.02,1:32:42.03,Default,,0,0,0,,the reason for it. It's just a fact. So you can, if you're really worried and cannot get
Dialogue: 0,1:32:42.03,1:32:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,off of it, you find some place that has the labyrinth in the parking lot or something,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:48.36,1:32:52.09,Default,,0,0,0,,or you get a copy of the labyrinth and you trace it slowly.
Dialogue: 0,1:32:52.25,1:32:59.60,Default,,0,0,0,,You trace it with the tip of a pencil and you follow. It says go this way, go this way,
Dialogue: 0,1:32:59.60,1:33:07.56,Default,,0,0,0,,now go this way, now go this way. There's something about this mysterious pattern that
Dialogue: 0,1:33:07.56,1:33:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,brings a profound sense of peace, a profound sense of peace from merely following a diagram
Dialogue: 0,1:33:14.02,1:33:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,with your eye or your pencil, or if it's large, walking it. Walk the labyrinth. Something
Dialogue: 0,1:33:23.50,1:33:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,similar is to do the rosary.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:25.89,1:33:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Do the rosary. Something similar is spinning the prayer wheel. Yes. All right, let's ask
Dialogue: 0,1:33:34.56,1:33:41.92,Default,,0,0,0,,if those all work. Doing the rosary brings about greater inner peace. Spinning the prayer
Dialogue: 0,1:33:41.92,1:33:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,wheel brings about greater inner peace. Resist. So whether you're Christian, Buddhist, or
Dialogue: 0,1:33:47.23,1:33:52.02,Default,,0,0,0,,whatever, it doesn't say you have to be a Christian or a believer to do these things.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:52.02,1:33:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,It just says do them. It doesn't say only Christians.
Dialogue: 0,1:33:57.05,1:34:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,The buddhists benefit from the labyrinth. Only buddhists benefit from the prayer wheel.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:01.94,1:34:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Says anybody, anybody. So there's something beyond belief systems. There's some other
Dialogue: 0,1:34:10.93,1:34:18.39,Default,,0,0,0,,power and energy and patterning in the universe, which nobody has discovered as yet. In my
Dialogue: 0,1:34:18.39,1:34:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,perusal of the world's spiritual literature over decades, I've never come across any explanation
Dialogue: 0,1:34:24.89,1:34:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,why such a geometric pattern.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:27.85,1:34:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,have such a profound effect.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.02,1:34:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,There is some recent
Dialogue: 0,1:34:31.90,1:34:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,research on the Taurus,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:33.60,1:34:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,T-O-R-U-S,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:36.06,1:34:37.43,Default,,0,0,0,,shape, and
Dialogue: 0,1:34:37.43,1:34:40.27,Default,,0,0,0,,in the mathematics
Dialogue: 0,1:34:40.27,1:34:42.09,Default,,0,0,0,,thereof, could be
Dialogue: 0,1:34:42.09,1:34:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,perhaps a plausible explanation,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:44.81,1:34:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,a partial explanation.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:46.67,1:34:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:47.64,1:34:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Do the rosary, walk the labyrinth,
Dialogue: 0,1:34:49.68,1:34:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,and spin the prayer wheel.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:51.93,1:34:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Another thing that will calm your nerves is to
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.15,1:34:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,write your will.
Dialogue: 0,1:34:54.85,1:34:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,And take out life insurance.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:01.61,1:35:02.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody here
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.19,1:35:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,lacks life insurance?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:05.10,1:35:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, uh-oh, uh-oh, uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:11.63,1:35:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Anybody here hasn't written a will?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:15.15,1:35:16.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh-oh, uh-oh, uh-oh, uh-oh.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:18.51,1:35:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,The fact that you're mortal
Dialogue: 0,1:35:20.92,1:35:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,and the acceptance
Dialogue: 0,1:35:23.18,1:35:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,of your mortality,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:25.68,1:35:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,therefore, to not
Dialogue: 0,1:35:28.06,1:35:29.93,Default,,0,0,0,,have a will, et cetera, no life
Dialogue: 0,1:35:29.93,1:35:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,insurance, means
Dialogue: 0,1:35:31.88,1:35:33.96,Default,,0,0,0,,a loss of sense of reality.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:35.42,1:35:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,In reality,
Dialogue: 0,1:35:36.61,1:35:38.02,Default,,0,0,0,,you're going to come to an end.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:39.27,1:35:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I hate to tell you that, but
Dialogue: 0,1:35:40.28,1:35:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is this news to anybody?
Dialogue: 0,1:35:44.69,1:35:46.93,Default,,0,0,0,,A few arms go up, yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:47.73,1:35:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It does come to an end, yes.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:50.69,1:35:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody you might as well benefit.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:52.46,1:35:53.61,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to croak anyway.
Dialogue: 0,1:35:56.71,1:35:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You watch on TV, you can get
Dialogue: 0,1:35:58.35,1:36:00.27,Default,,0,0,0,,life insurance pretty darn cheap nowadays.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:02.23,1:36:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Kick out a friend,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:03.18,1:36:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,a relative, leave it
Dialogue: 0,1:36:05.31,1:36:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,to the humane society.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:08.01,1:36:09.35,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't have any friends,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:09.35,1:36:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,your relatives, what about
Dialogue: 0,1:36:11.39,1:36:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,all the little doggies and kitties
Dialogue: 0,1:36:13.01,1:36:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,that have no home?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:14.85,1:36:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You can make out a will and leave
Dialogue: 0,1:36:17.01,1:36:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,a life insurance policy to the humane society.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:19.94,1:36:20.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:21.40,1:36:23.25,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the importance of those things?
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.44,1:36:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Because there's a certain generosity,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:27.21,1:36:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,a lovingness,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:29.48,1:36:30.28,Default,,0,0,0,,that your death
Dialogue: 0,1:36:30.28,1:36:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,will serve some positive benefit
Dialogue: 0,1:36:32.27,1:36:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,to life in its various forms.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:35.40,1:36:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,The humane society
Dialogue: 0,1:36:36.31,1:36:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,could use the insurance money
Dialogue: 0,1:36:38.05,1:36:39.98,Default,,0,0,0,,so it can,
Dialogue: 0,1:36:40.14,1:36:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,find more homes for more homeless pets, et cetera.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:44.93,1:36:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Write a will, take out life insurance.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:48.42,1:36:50.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Watch television's Animal Channel.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:50.69,1:36:54.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Animal Channel has very interesting things on it, yep.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:54.22,1:36:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And bury the hatchet.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:56.43,1:36:59.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Bury the hatchet.
Dialogue: 0,1:36:59.15,1:37:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I went to a camp, and when the boys
Dialogue: 0,1:37:00.96,1:37:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,were getting to scrabble with each other,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:02.31,1:37:04.30,Default,,0,0,0,,at midnight, they'd all get off to get up.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:04.30,1:37:06.81,Default,,0,0,0,,You had to go out and dig a hole.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:06.81,1:37:08.61,Default,,0,0,0,,And you had to put your hatchet in there,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:08.61,1:37:10.02,Default,,0,0,0,,and then bury it.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:10.02,1:37:12.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That was a new thing.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:12.07,1:37:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Who wants to get up at midnight
Dialogue: 0,1:37:14.07,1:37:16.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and go dig a hole in the dark?
Dialogue: 0,1:37:16.07,1:37:18.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We were all scared of the dark anyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:18.07,1:37:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,because we were all about 12 or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:20.07,1:37:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,So we learned how to avoid
Dialogue: 0,1:37:24.39,1:37:27.06,Default,,0,0,0,,needing to bury the hatchet.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:27.06,1:37:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Give up being an adrenaline junkie.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:29.06,1:37:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a hard one.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:31.13,1:37:33.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You see all these speeders, you know,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:33.13,1:37:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,they're caught going 110 on the parkway.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:35.13,1:37:37.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They're always in Los Angeles,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:37.13,1:37:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and they're always going 100.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:39.13,1:37:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And you see the helicopter
Dialogue: 0,1:37:41.13,1:37:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,following them hour after hour.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:43.13,1:37:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Finally, you get so bored
Dialogue: 0,1:37:45.73,1:37:47.73,Default,,0,0,0,,of watching this stupid driver,
Dialogue: 0,1:37:47.73,1:37:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready to punch him in the mouth
Dialogue: 0,1:37:49.73,1:37:52.40,Default,,0,0,0,,when he gets out of his car.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:52.40,1:37:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Shat three hours of my life on television.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:54.40,1:37:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't quit until I found out
Dialogue: 0,1:37:56.40,1:37:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,whether this guy was caught.
Dialogue: 0,1:37:58.40,1:38:02.23,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's almost a psychopath.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:02.23,1:38:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,The last time, I think, it was a woman.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:05.10,1:38:07.10,Default,,0,0,0,,People think, oh, women don't do that.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:07.10,1:38:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're women psychopaths, too.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:09.10,1:38:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,On dope and an adrenaline junkie.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:11.10,1:38:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, one thing of importance
Dialogue: 0,1:38:13.10,1:38:15.47,Default,,0,0,0,,is to keep your head up.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:15.47,1:38:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,One thing of importance
Dialogue: 0,1:38:17.47,1:38:19.86,Default,,0,0,0,,is to quit when you're ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:19.86,1:38:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit when you're ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.86,1:38:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,People push the greed button to the point
Dialogue: 0,1:38:23.89,1:38:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,100,000 a year isn't enough.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:25.89,1:38:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta push, push, push, push.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.89,1:38:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Push to 105, push to 110.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:29.89,1:38:31.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, then they get fired.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.89,1:38:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit when you're ahead.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:35.89,1:38:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go of greed.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:37.89,1:38:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the hard one.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:39.89,1:38:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,And greed is that rapacious
Dialogue: 0,1:38:41.89,1:38:43.89,Default,,0,0,0,,wantingness.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:43.89,1:38:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Woke your Buddha nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:46.43,1:38:48.43,Default,,0,0,0,,And cleverly live in the space
Dialogue: 0,1:38:48.43,1:38:50.43,Default,,0,0,0,,beneath thoughts.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:50.43,1:38:52.43,Default,,0,0,0,,People say, how can I get the mind
Dialogue: 0,1:38:52.43,1:38:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,to stop?
Dialogue: 0,1:38:54.43,1:38:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You don't have to get the mind to stop.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:56.43,1:38:59.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Just pay no attention to it.
Dialogue: 0,1:38:59.47,1:39:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll notice that thoughts are like
Dialogue: 0,1:39:01.47,1:39:03.47,Default,,0,0,0,,the surface of the sea.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:03.47,1:39:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,And beneath the surface of the sea
Dialogue: 0,1:39:05.47,1:39:08.17,Default,,0,0,0,,is the stillness of the deep.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:08.17,1:39:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Beneath thoughts, there is absolute silence.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:10.17,1:39:12.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Right now, this voice
Dialogue: 0,1:39:12.35,1:39:15.03,Default,,0,0,0,,is talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:15.03,1:39:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,With spiritual advancement,
Dialogue: 0,1:39:17.03,1:39:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aware that everything is happening
Dialogue: 0,1:39:19.03,1:39:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,autonomously of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:21.03,1:39:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have to talk.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:23.68,1:39:25.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The talkingness is happening, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,1:39:25.68,1:39:31.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The talkingness is happening
Dialogue: 0,1:39:31.57,1:39:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:34.31,1:39:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need a me that's talking.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:36.31,1:39:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I just witness that talkingness
Dialogue: 0,1:39:38.31,1:39:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,is happening of its own.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:40.31,1:39:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So most of the things
Dialogue: 0,1:39:44.32,1:39:46.32,Default,,0,0,0,,we worry about and take blame for
Dialogue: 0,1:39:46.32,1:39:48.32,Default,,0,0,0,,and feel guilty over
Dialogue: 0,1:39:48.32,1:39:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,are frankly autonomous.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:50.32,1:39:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Autonomous.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:52.32,1:39:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,They happen of their own nature.
Dialogue: 0,1:39:54.48,1:39:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Just like a seed opens up
Dialogue: 0,1:39:56.48,1:39:58.48,Default,,0,0,0,,in sprouts of its own nature
Dialogue: 0,1:39:58.48,1:40:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,when it's time for it to do so.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:00.48,1:40:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,So there's no point of hovering over it,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:02.48,1:40:04.48,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to hurry it up,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:04.48,1:40:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,or trying to slow it down.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:06.48,1:40:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,In its own due time,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:08.48,1:40:10.48,Default,,0,0,0,,which is karmically determined,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:10.48,1:40:12.48,Default,,0,0,0,,including when you leave
Dialogue: 0,1:40:12.48,1:40:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,this world.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:14.48,1:40:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,And when you leave this world,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:16.93,1:40:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,we've done this before,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:18.93,1:40:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,let's just do it again.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:21.60,1:40:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,From the moment of birth on,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:23.60,1:40:25.60,Default,,0,0,0,,of when you leave this world,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:25.60,1:40:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,it's already preset.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:27.60,1:40:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,We're worrying about dying
Dialogue: 0,1:40:30.43,1:40:32.43,Default,,0,0,0,,because it's already certified,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.43,1:40:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,signed, sealed, delivered, and stamped.
Dialogue: 0,1:40:37.85,1:40:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean
Dialogue: 0,1:40:40.10,1:40:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,you should be careless,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:42.10,1:40:44.10,Default,,0,0,0,,go out and get drunk,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:44.10,1:40:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,and drive at 150 miles an hour
Dialogue: 0,1:40:46.23,1:40:50.31,Default,,0,0,0,,down the speedway,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.31,1:40:52.31,Default,,0,0,0,,trying to disprove it?
Dialogue: 0,1:40:52.31,1:40:54.31,Default,,0,0,0,,No, because it was destined
Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.31,1:40:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,that you would get drunk,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.31,1:40:59.31,Default,,0,0,0,,drive 150 miles down the speedway,
Dialogue: 0,1:40:59.31,1:41:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,and turn your car over.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:03.68,1:41:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Once in a while,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:05.68,1:41:07.68,Default,,0,0,0,,I get an inquiry by email.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:07.68,1:41:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,If the time of your leaving is preset,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:09.68,1:41:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,why bother with caution?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:11.68,1:41:13.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Why bother with safety
Dialogue: 0,1:41:13.68,1:41:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,if it's all set?
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.68,1:41:17.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's fatalism,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:17.73,1:41:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,something different.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.73,1:41:22.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:22.02,1:41:24.02,Default,,0,0,0,,stop trying to make it logical.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:24.02,1:41:26.02,Default,,0,0,0,,All we know is that
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.02,1:41:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,every time we pass this over the years,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:28.02,1:41:30.02,Default,,0,0,0,,the wind of your leaving
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.02,1:41:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,is preset.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.02,1:41:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been preset
Dialogue: 0,1:41:34.02,1:41:36.02,Default,,0,0,0,,since the beginning of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:36.02,1:41:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:39.43,1:41:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Preset since the beginning of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:41.43,1:41:44.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The time you leave this earth
Dialogue: 0,1:41:44.97,1:41:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,is preset since the beginning of time.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:46.97,1:41:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Resist.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:51.85,1:41:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:53.85,1:41:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,it's because each one of us
Dialogue: 0,1:41:55.85,1:41:57.85,Default,,0,0,0,,is part of God's creation.
Dialogue: 0,1:41:57.85,1:41:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,From the beginning of all time,
Dialogue: 0,1:41:59.85,1:42:02.17,Default,,0,0,0,,the beginning of creation,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:02.17,1:42:04.84,Default,,0,0,0,,there's not a then and a now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:04.84,1:42:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,In the infinite world
Dialogue: 0,1:42:06.84,1:42:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:09.22,1:42:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,all places are here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:11.26,1:42:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,All time is now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.39,1:42:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,There is nothing like then
Dialogue: 0,1:42:17.14,1:42:19.14,Default,,0,0,0,,and now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:19.14,1:42:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything is now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:21.94,1:42:23.94,Default,,0,0,0,,In an infinite field of consciousness,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:23.94,1:42:25.94,Default,,0,0,0,,there's no here or there.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:25.94,1:42:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Every place is equally the center.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:27.94,1:42:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Every place is equally here.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:29.97,1:42:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Any point in time
Dialogue: 0,1:42:32.23,1:42:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,is now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:34.68,1:42:36.68,Default,,0,0,0,,As you can see,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:36.68,1:42:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,when you're dealing with infinity,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:38.68,1:42:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,all the usual logic of thought
Dialogue: 0,1:42:40.68,1:42:43.10,Default,,0,0,0,,is thrown out the window.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:43.10,1:42:46.00,Default,,0,0,0,,All time is now.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:46.00,1:42:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,When you get crazy,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:48.47,1:42:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,and everybody gets crazy,
Dialogue: 0,1:42:50.47,1:42:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,anybody here thinks they don't get crazy
Dialogue: 0,1:42:52.47,1:42:54.69,Default,,0,0,0,,periodically?
Dialogue: 0,1:42:54.69,1:42:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,1:42:56.80,1:43:00.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotta be a nut job out there somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:00.39,1:43:02.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiding in your seat will do no good.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:02.46,1:43:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you're out there.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:04.46,1:43:13.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak sanely to yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:43:13.27,1:43:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:16.10,1:43:18.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I look at myself in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:18.10,1:43:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I can vaguely see myself anymore.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:20.10,1:43:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,I see some older, I say,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:22.56,1:43:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,God, you're looking like,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:24.56,1:43:27.26,Default,,0,0,0,,you're starting to look like an old duck or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:27.26,1:43:29.26,Default,,0,0,0,,My hair's getting thin on top, for God's sake.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:29.26,1:43:31.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I can see.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:31.73,1:43:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It's this fuzzy grayness.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:33.73,1:43:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,It seems to be getting bald up here.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:35.73,1:43:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't see it before.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:38.76,1:43:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,There's one bathroom that has light over it.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:40.76,1:43:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,The first time I looked at it,
Dialogue: 0,1:43:42.82,1:43:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,I said, my God, he's losing his hair
Dialogue: 0,1:43:44.82,1:43:50.06,Default,,0,0,0,,on the top of his bloody head.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:52.85,1:43:54.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I was shocked to see that.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:54.85,1:43:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I still had the image
Dialogue: 0,1:43:57.63,1:43:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,of when I was in the 30s or something.
Dialogue: 0,1:43:59.63,1:44:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Big mop of hair, you know.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:01.63,1:44:03.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Everybody had moppy hair in those days.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:03.63,1:44:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Speak sanely to yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:44:05.65,1:44:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:07.65,1:44:09.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Give yourself a lecture
Dialogue: 0,1:44:09.76,1:44:11.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and be kind to yourself
Dialogue: 0,1:44:11.92,1:44:13.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and realize that you are crazier
Dialogue: 0,1:44:13.92,1:44:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,than a loon
Dialogue: 0,1:44:15.92,1:44:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,and stupider than hell.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:22.10,1:44:24.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The truth, buddy,
Dialogue: 0,1:44:24.64,1:44:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,is that you are a nut job
Dialogue: 0,1:44:26.64,1:44:29.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and you're not too bright
Dialogue: 0,1:44:29.52,1:44:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,and how God tolerates your existence
Dialogue: 0,1:44:31.52,1:44:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,in the universe
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.55,1:44:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,is simply the consequence
Dialogue: 0,1:44:35.55,1:44:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,that he created you.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:39.21,1:44:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,I know God can't throw me out the window
Dialogue: 0,1:44:41.21,1:44:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,because I'm his handiwork.
Dialogue: 0,1:44:58.75,1:45:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Right about face, right about face.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:00.75,1:45:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, in the winning circle,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:03.77,1:45:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,there I am in the winning circle
Dialogue: 0,1:45:07.23,1:45:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,talking to myself in the mirror.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:12.10,1:45:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,And the other thing,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:14.90,1:45:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,as I've said earlier in these things,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:16.93,1:45:18.93,Default,,0,0,0,,always have a counselor,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:18.93,1:45:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,a confidant,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:20.93,1:45:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,a therapist,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:22.93,1:45:24.93,Default,,0,0,0,,a psychologist,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:24.93,1:45:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a best friend,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:27.10,1:45:29.10,Default,,0,0,0,,people that you can rely on,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:29.10,1:45:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,a great spouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:31.10,1:45:37.68,Default,,0,0,0,,A great spouse.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:47.60,1:45:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,As you notice,
Dialogue: 0,1:45:49.60,1:45:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a great person.
Dialogue: 0,1:45:53.31,1:45:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, what happens next
Dialogue: 0,1:45:55.31,1:45:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,because I turned it over to you
Dialogue: 0,1:45:57.31,1:46:00.17,Default,,0,0,0,,at this point.
